headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid LH and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Labcorp has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 6.9%. Its stock price has climbed to $255.01, representing a healthy 13.9% increase. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
